[
  {
    "text": "Jacob Klapper: Hi! Welcome to What's New in Sharing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Jacob Klapper, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm an engineer on the Share Sheet team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's dive right in and take a look ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=8"
  },
  {
    "text": "at the new Share Sheet in iOS 13. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Share Sheet features a new preview header at the top. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "This makes it clear what the user is sharing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "and allows them to customize it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "The new Share Sheet also makes it easier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "to share quickly and effortlessly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the conversation suggestions row ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "that predicts who users will want to share to. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, the new actions list ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "offers a clear delineation between apps and actions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "and puts users' favorite actions at the top for easy access. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's talk about how you can take advantage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "of this new design to enhance your users' sharing experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "First we'll talk about customizing the preview header ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we'll go over opting in to conversation suggestions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your messaging app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, we'll review some best practices. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, let's talk about how to configure a preview header ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=53"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS 13 introduces the LinkPresentation API ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "that allows you to present rich links in your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "UIActivityViewController takes advantage of this framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "to display the preview header in the Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "This makes it clear to the user ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "what they're sharing from your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "As an added benefit, when users share via Messages, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "the link preview in the transcript ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "will match the one from the Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "This adds continuity to the users' sharing experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at the preview header in Safari.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "It looks pretty good right now, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "but the Share Sheet had to fetch the website information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "to be displayed in the header. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's watch again.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not right for the Share Sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "to have to fetch this information, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "because Safari likely has it already. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "To accelerate the preview, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "Safari can use UIActivityItemSource ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "to give the Share Sheet LinkPresentation metadata ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "to be displayed in the header. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an example of the new ActivityViewContoller ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "link metadata method on UIActivityItemSource. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, create an LPLinkMetadata object. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then set the originalURL and URL properties. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "Set a title and iconProvider. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, return the metadata. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see what the preview header looks like now. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you can see, all the information was available immediately, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the Share Sheet didn't have to do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "any additional metadata fetching. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's talk about the new conversation suggestions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Share Sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "Conversation suggestions allow users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "to effortlessly send content to specific recipients ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "without having to type their names. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "While conversation suggestions utilize SiriKit Intents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "you do not need to add a SiriKit UI Extension ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "or provide Siri support for suggestions to work. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "The conversation suggestions row is conveniently placed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "at the top of the Share Sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "so users will be able to launch your share extension ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a simple tap. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's talk about how to opt in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "your messaging app's share extension to suggestions. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "Donate INSendMessageIntents on message sends from app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "and share extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "In order to provide users with a richer experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure to populate as many fields as possible, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "including, but not limited to: recipients, speakableGroupName, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "and conversationIdentifier. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "When your share extension is launched, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "the intent property on NSExtensionContext ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "will provide information about the conversation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "to populate your UI with. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "The final step is to add INSendMessageIntent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the IntentsSupported array ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your share extension's Info.plist ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at an example INSendMessageIntent donation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "This function should be called ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "every time a user sends a message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your app or share extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "A conversation identifier helps the Share Sheet ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "identify the recipients or groups ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will be receiving the message. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "The group name will be used to display ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "the conversation in the Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case, the participants array ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "is an array of INPerson objects. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each INPerson should have a display name and an image ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "so users can easily spot them in the Share Sheet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, create an INInteraction using the sendMessageIntent. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "Set the direction as outgoing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "because the user is sending the message in this case. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, donate the interaction. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "The IntentsSupported array should be inserted ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the NSExtensionAttributes dictionary ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your Share Extension's Info.plist. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure INSendMessageIntent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "is listed as one of the supported intents, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "or conversation suggestions will not be enabled ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you have completed all of the steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "to opt in your share extension ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will begin to see suggestions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "for recipients linked with your share extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "The suggestion features a contact or group image ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "and display name, along with your app's icon, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "so your users can easily identify it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's finish up by going over some best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=289"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the Share Sheet.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, let's talk about how to optimize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "your action extension icons for the new actions list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, icons should be 40 by 40 template images. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "They should be outlined glyphs without fill ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "to match the system icons. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=309"
  },
  {
    "text": "When possible, use SF Symbols or symbol images. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do this, add the CFBundleSymbolName key ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your action extension's Info.plist. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, let's talk about card UI. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "New in iOS 13, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "share extensions will be presented as form sheets. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your share extension requires full-screen presentation, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can opt in using ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "the NSExtensionShareWants FullScreenPresentation key ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your extension's Info.plist. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=339"
  },
  {
    "text": "Most extensions shouldn't need this, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "but a good example of one that would ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "is an extension that needs to use the camera.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, I want to go over some new behavior ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "for share extensions in iOS 13. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "Share Extensions are now displayed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "using their containing app's display name, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "not the extension's display name. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app has multiple share extensions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "it will be difficult for users to differentiate them. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "Because of this, your app should limit itself ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a single share extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app had multiple share extensions previously, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can consolidate them into one by adding an options UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "to allow your user to select which functionality they want ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they launch your share extension. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-210/?time=379"
  },
